now with big-ass blonds.

07:01.797 --> 07:04.508
Heh, heh. Yeah. You can't swim.

07:05.259 --> 07:06.802
You would've drowned.

07:06.969 --> 07:10.055
On that note, I'll leave you
with the blonds you'll never have.

07:10.222 --> 07:13.142
Tell Mr. Sandpaper Hands
I want my two sleeping pills.

07:13.308 --> 07:15.310
-It's 10 in the morning.
- Then I want four.

07:15.477 --> 07:18.689
I wanna be dreaming of all them hookers
that you deprived me of.

07:18.856 --> 07:19.982
[CHUCKLES]

07:27.072 --> 07:28.198
Hey!

07:29.324 --> 07:32.411
Hey, you can't park here.

07:33.120 --> 07:35.706
Take it easy, man.
I'm the Ghost of Christmas Present.

07:35.873 --> 07:36.915
Really?

07:37.291 --> 07:39.334
Oh, come on, Razor. Razor.

07:40.335 --> 07:43.881
It's Dante Jr. Don't act like
I didn't grow up to be a fine looking man.

07:44.047 --> 07:46.091
Right. Too bad your father
didn't show up...

07:46.258 --> 07:49.386
...so I can belt him
for taking what was left of my purses.

07:49.845 --> 07:53.557
- Dad passed away last year.
- If you didn't see him dead, I wouldn't trust that.

07:53.724 --> 07:54.975
I did.

07:57.895 --> 07:59.563
Now you make me feel a little bad.

08:00.272 --> 08:03.066
- Wanna come in or something?
- I would love to come in, Razor.

08:03.484 --> 08:07.821
You look good. Hey, should I roll my
window up? Is this a good area?

08:09.865 --> 08:13.494
Tuna fish, some overripe bananas
that you probably bought on sale.

08:13.660 --> 08:14.786
You shop like my grandmom.

08:14.953 --> 08:18.665
Bananas are a good source of potassium
and I had double coupons for the fish.

08:18.832 --> 08:22.920
That's not fish. Fish is like a sushi.
That's a step above cat food, Razor.

08:23.086 --> 08:26.924
It's dolphin safe and I don't sweat
the extra nickel because it's the right thing.

08:27.466 --> 08:29.218
Not my business. Your house, sorry.

08:29.760 --> 08:31.678
What is this?
It's like a mouse or something?

08:31.845 --> 08:32.929
- What is that?
RAZOR: A dog.

08:33.096 --> 08:35.349
- A dog?
-It's a dog.

08:35.515 --> 08:38.434
- So why you here, Junior?
- Why am I here?

08:40.187 --> 08:41.522
You know what this is, Razor?

08:41.688 --> 08:43.273
A bad movie?

08:43.440 --> 08:45.108
-It's a video game.
- Right.

08:45.275 --> 08:47.361
When did they unfreeze you,
Captain America?

08:47.945 --> 08:50.864
"Captain America"?
You know, I'd like to take you down a peg...

08:51.031 --> 08:53.200
...but it looks like somebody beat me to it.

08:53.867 --> 08:56.411
A height joke.
That was good. That's original.

08:56.578 --> 08:58.372
Height ain't nothing but a number.

08:58.539 --> 09:01.583
See, in Thailand, I'm in the 95th percentile.
I'm okay over there.

09:01.750 --> 09:04.419
So, what you say can't hurt my feelings.
Let's talk turkey.

09:04.586 --> 09:06.880
The guys that made this game
saw your HBO special.

09:07.047 --> 09:09.841
They loved it. I loved it.
Did I tell you? I really did.

09:10.008 --> 09:11.969
Anyway,
they wanna put you and Kid in the game.

09:12.135 --> 09:14.304
Okay?
Before you say anything, hear me out.

09:14.471 --> 09:18.392
All they do is videotape you throwing
a couple punches, record you making noises.

09:18.559 --> 09:20.811
Unh! Unh! Ugh! I'm gonna kill you.

09:20.978 --> 09:23.397
Except in a white guy's voice.
They don't wanna scare anybody.

09:23.564 --> 09:25.524
- That's how simple this is.
- It ain't that simple.

09:25.691 --> 09:29.528
- I can't be in the same room as that guy.
- Okay, okay. Now listen. Slow down.

09:29.695 --> 09:31.947
That's the case,
I'll bring you in on separate days.

09:32.114 --> 09:34.533
You're talking less than an hour for 10 grand.

09:35.117 --> 09:37.494
Ten grand, man. Easy.

09:37.953 --> 09:39.913
No. Not worth it.

09:40.872 --> 09:43.834
The hell you mean, it ain't worth it?
I'm looking at your house!

09:44.001 --> 09:45.586
No. You're obviously doing well...

09:45.752 --> 09:48.755
...with all this F-you mouse sculpture
making money you got.

09:48.922 --> 09:51.174
It's a dog and I don't do it for money.

09:51.341 --> 09:53.635
Tell you what, you wanna play hardball?
Twelve Gs.

09:53.802 --> 09:55.971
Twelve Gs. I pulled it out my ass.
Twelve Gs.

09:56.138 --> 09:58.515
I'll get 12 Gs,
you knickknack-making son of a bitch.

10:04.187 --> 10:06.440
I don't like the way you looking at me, as if...

10:08.275 --> 10:10.360
Stubborn piece of shit.

10:10.527 --> 10:13.030
You were right to rip him off, Daddy.
You should've.

10:13.614 --> 10:17.409
Come here with a perfectly damn good deal,
you gonna throw it back in my face?

10:17.576 --> 10:20.871
Like I'm crazy? Okay. That's fine.

10:22.205 --> 10:24.082
[ENGINE SPUTTERING]

10:25.292 --> 10:26.793
Piece of shit!

10:28.045 --> 10:29.880
