10:47.397 --> 10:49.900
Done and done. That is done.

10:50.067 --> 10:51.485
Ha, ha.

10:51.652 --> 10:54.196
Hey, Raze, real quick.
Do you got any jumper cables?

10:54.946 --> 10:56.573
You think you can give me a jump?

10:56.740 --> 10:57.783
No.

10:58.533 --> 10:59.660
Okay, it's fine.

10:59.826 --> 11:00.952
