12:49.227 --> 12:52.189
- What'd I tell you? I told you to come in 1:00.
- I came early.

12:52.355 --> 12:55.567
I wanted to see my old friend.
He's been ducking me 30 years. I missed him.

12:55.734 --> 12:58.528
