I'm out of here.

12:58.695 --> 13:02.699
No, you're not. Not till you admit
that you quit because you were scared of me.

13:02.866 --> 13:04.701
- Why do you talk like that?
- What do you mean?

13:04.868 --> 13:06.995
- Just admit it. It's true.
- You know what?

13:07.162 --> 13:09.122
I'm getting out of here, and I'm asking nice.

13:09.289 --> 13:10.874
- Or what?
- Just get out of the way.

13:11.041 --> 13:15.378
Listen. Those punches might get these nerds
all hot under the pants, but you know what?

13:15.545 --> 13:19.549
They're the same half-assed punches you
threw 30 years ago when you ran from me.

13:19.716 --> 13:22.385
- Move, or I'm moving you.
- Try and move me. Go ahead.

13:23.470 --> 13:26.640
You know, maybe you're right.
I might pop a disc, you're just so fat.

13:26.807 --> 13:28.683
What weight class you fighting at now,
LAP-BAND?

13:28.850 --> 13:32.187
- I can still take you.
- Maybe to the prom if you ask nice.

13:32.354 --> 13:33.897
- Pushing your luck now.
- Hey! Hey!

13:34.064 --> 13:35.065
I'm sorry.

13:35.232 --> 13:38.068
- I'm sorry. I did it to you, all right?
RAZOR: You're just sorry?

13:38.235 --> 13:39.736
You're a lucky guy.

13:39.903 --> 13:42.405
No, no. No! No, man! What are you doing?

13:42.572 --> 13:44.658
- No, no. Razor!
MAN: What you doing with that?

13:44.825 --> 13:46.535
- Stop! Stop it!
MAN: Oh, man.

13:46.701 --> 13:48.703
[BOTH GRUNTING]

13:49.329 --> 13:51.248
