14:58.315 --> 15:00.984
Huh? You can't ignore me.
Can't ignore me.

15:01.151 --> 15:03.570
Will one of you hurry up
and rape this guy, already?

15:04.154 --> 15:05.655
[ALL LAUGH]

15:06.573 --> 15:08.992
Yo, Sharp, McDonnen.
You made bail.

15:11.786 --> 15:14.998
Soon as we get out of these cops' eyelines,
I'm gonna punch you again.

15:15.165 --> 15:16.833
Tell me so I know when to say "Ow."

15:17.000 --> 15:20.170
Ladies! My God, please don't embarrass
yourselves any further out here.

15:20.337 --> 15:22.005
Come look at this. Look at this video.

15:22.172 --> 15:23.882
- What's this?
-It's going viral.

15:24.049 --> 15:26.343
It's got over,
like, a million views right now.

15:26.509 --> 15:28.678
You don't know what I mean
by "going viral."

15:28.845 --> 15:30.513
Razor, you know what YouTube is?

15:30.680 --> 15:34.517
Neither one of you know what "viral" means?
What type of two out-of-touch, old--

15:34.684 --> 15:35.769
-Hey.
-Hey.

15:35.936 --> 15:37.729
Sorry. No, no. Uncalled-for. Forget it.

15:37.896 --> 15:41.274
- Look, it's a video of your fight.
KID: That's me? Hey, that's me.

15:41.441 --> 15:44.861
- They say the camera adds 10 pounds.
- What's your excuse for the other 20?

15:45.028 --> 15:47.781
Do me a favor? Save the verbal jousting
for a more important time.

15:47.948 --> 15:49.658
I'm about to lay something huge on you.

15:49.824 --> 15:53.036
I got a company that wants the rematch.
December 15th, Palace Theatre.

15:53.203 --> 15:55.664
- They want to pay each of us 75 grand.
- Each of us?

15:55.830 --> 15:58.500
I meant each of you.
They're gonna pay you 100 grand.

15:58.667 --> 16:03.171
- You just said 75. Now you went to 100?
- I was thinking about the thing at the house.

16:03.338 --> 16:04.965
Don't worry, it ain't gonna happen.

16:05.131 --> 16:07.550
Just give me the 15 grand you promised
for the game.

16:07.717 --> 16:09.678
Hey, jagoff, you promised him 15 grand?

16:09.844 --> 16:11.054
He did. Give me the money.

16:11.221 --> 16:12.555
They're not gonna pay you.

16:12.722 --> 16:15.141
Lucky if they don't sue
for breaking the equip--

16:15.308 --> 16:18.061
- I needed that money.
- I should be doing this for the 15.

16:18.228 --> 16:20.689
You should get off me
in front of this police station.

16:20.855 --> 16:24.401
- I got more money for you.
- Nothing you could offer me. I ain't fighting.

16:24.567 --> 16:25.902
You're still a chickenshit.

16:26.069 --> 16:28.488
- Razor, don't walk away.
KID: Why don't you wanna do it?

16:28.655 --> 16:31.074
- Please.
-It's a chance of a lifetime, you moron.

16:31.241 --> 16:32.409
DANTE:
Not helping. Razor!

16:32.575 --> 16:35.537
- What are you provoking him for?
KID: I'm not. I didn't do anything.

16:35.704 --> 16:40.000
Well, I did do something,
but that's a long time ago.

16:40.583 --> 16:42.585
And that's probably what it is.

16:44.879 --> 16:46.548
I banged his girlfriend.

16:46.715 --> 16:49.718
- I'm sorry, what?
- I knocked her up. His girlfriend.

16:49.884 --> 16:52.387
Great segue into information
I needed to know earlier.

16:52.554 --> 16:54.723
Probably wasn't a good idea.

16:55.640 --> 16:58.059
A momentary lapse in judgment.

16:58.226 --> 16:59.561
I'll say.

16:59.728 --> 17:02.522
