That's what you--

17:02.689 --> 17:06.067
I can't-- This is white people shit, man.

17:08.111 --> 17:10.696
Son of a bitch. He ain't ever gonna fight me.

17:10.864 --> 17:12.949
Can't believe you would. It's insane.

17:13.116 --> 17:16.286
Oh, yeah? What? Give me one reason.

17:16.453 --> 17:18.454
You're old. You're fat.

17:18.621 --> 17:21.124
You got a bad back.
You got weak knees.

17:21.290 --> 17:22.291
You're fat.

17:22.459 --> 17:25.127
Hey, you know, don't sugarcoat it.
Be honest.

17:28.923 --> 17:30.633
Ah...

17:30.925 --> 17:32.927
It ain't gonna happen anyway.

17:33.303 --> 17:34.471
It's never gonna happen.

17:34.637 --> 17:36.639
Thank God for that.

17:48.693 --> 17:50.403
Walter, where you going?

17:50.570 --> 17:54.282
More layoffs, man.
After 30 years, they let me go just like that.

17:54.449 --> 17:55.492
